  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18 and older

          -  Undergoing a dermatologic procedure

          -  Willing and able to understand and provide informed consent and communicate with the
             investigator

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects who have wound healing problems

          -  Subjects who are unable to understand the protocol or to give informed consent

          -  Subjects with self-reported mental illness or other psychological conditions, such as
             psychotic disorders, mood disorders, anxiety disorders, cognitive disorders,
             depression with psychotic features, dissociative disorders
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
